sets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">任職車行的車主莫先生</span><br />\n<br />\n3日後有部特價Benz 出售 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"女車主，少揸，長泊室內，直版任驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68c5edbcd9af4d714a9fd92b0030506087b59b6","tid":2495064,"uid":103916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"90f5b754f654a19d64b10b07e24546b19caf17dc","tid":2495064,"uid":70964,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4a833efebda4a23e29a0ec742b98fe02f27556ad","tid":2495064,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:26:13.000Z","msg":"☰<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n即時新聞&nbsp;-&nbsp;港聞<br />\n<br />\n深水埗爆鹹水管射爆車窗 平治司機：年初花逾10萬購買<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-19 08:55<br />\n<br />\n￼￼平治私家車，車窗及天窗損毀。<br />\n<br />\n￼￼<br />\n<br />\n深水埗東京街及通州街交界凌晨有地底鹹水管爆裂，大量鹹水夾雜泥石湧出路面，噴出的水柱高約8米，達3層樓高。濺起的碎石疑擊中泊於附近的一輛平治私家車，車窗及天窗損毀，大量鹹水射入車內。<br />\n<br />\n任職車行的車主莫先生獲知事件後，返回現場善後。據悉，他昨晚11時左右將車泊於現場，其平治座駕於農曆新年前花10多萬元購買，無辜遭殃後或需換車，並<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">考慮會否追究水務署。</span></span><br />\n現場為富昌邨旁一條行人路。警方指，事發於凌晨4時33分，水管爆裂後，鹹水滲出行人道，影響範圍約10米乘10米。水柱濺起的碎石疑擊中停泊於現場的一輛私家車，其車窗及天窗損毀。事發後，水務署派員關上水掣及搶修。<br />\n<br />\n受事件影響，水務署網站顯示，富昌邨、榮昌邨、西邨路及西九龍法院大樓暫停鹹水供應，預計下午2時過後恢復供水。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2050170/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E7%88%86%E9%B9%B9%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E5%B0%84%E7%88%86%E8%BB%8A%E7%AA%97-%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%BE10%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2050170%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%25B9%25B9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25AA%2597-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%259D%25E8%258A%25B1%25E9%2580%25BE10%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=5583c4a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2050170%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E7%2588%2586%25E9%25B9%25B9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25AA%2597-%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%259D%25E8%258A%25B1%25E9%2580%25BE10%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25B2%25B7&h=f717434f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2050170/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E7%88%86%E9%B9%B9%E6%B0%B4%E7%AE%A1%E5%B0%84%E7%88%86%E8%BB%8A%E7%AA%97-%E5%B9%B3%E6%B2%BB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E8%8A%B1%E9%80%BE10%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"政府: 你唔泊O個度咪冇事 你自身問題唔賠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"違例泊車啊，比告票。"},{"pid":"8e9c14b2e530ec9f0933e3f7b451cd7d2c97b0ab","tid":2495064,"uid":170896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:41:30.000Z","msg":"比張告票佢啦<br />\n咁撚串"},{"pid":"7d43d3870c9c72c27c47d600030e38426da4a2de","tid":2495064,"uid":9116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:41:53.000Z","msg":"仲要泊起緊急車輛通道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過咁，其實係可以向港共索償，就算佢泊得幾閪都好，財物被損毀就應該去追討返"},{"pid":"9217144b0314a7959d96bd87c9bc37e5cdc7cbe6","tid":2495064,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime